{"tid":1767496,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"繼天津物產後 大型國企北大方正 首現債券違約 稱流動資金緊張","createTime":"2019-12-03T10:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T02:09:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb8157bde3ad53512223feafe5cdcddb704c9e8","tid":1767496,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】國有控股以及校企背景的中國北大方正集團公布，其一筆20億元(人民幣．下同)的超短期融資債券未能如期還本付息，為其首次債券違約。<br />\n<br />\n根據公告，這筆超短期融資券的債券發行總額是20億元，利率4.94厘，債券期限是270天。<br />\n<br />\n北大方正表示，因流動資金緊張，於截至周一，未能按照約定籌措足額資金償付本息。公司正在通過各種途徑積極籌措資金，並加強自身經營，努力保障本期超短期融資券的本息償付。<br />\n<br />\n北大方正稱，公司將保持與債券持有人及主承銷商等其他中介機構密切溝通，做好相關後續違約處理工作，並持續、及時、準確披露違約事項處置進展情況。<br />\n<br />\n北大方正是北京大學於1986年投資創辦的大型國有控股企業集團，旗下有方正科技、方正控股(00418)、方正證券等多家上市公司。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據報，北大方正還有未到期債券23隻，餘額總計345.4億元，其中未來一年內到期餘額為235.9億元，償付壓力較大。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/551115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F551115&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=d14722aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/551115</a><br />\n<br />\n上一單<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/11/27/chinas-tewoo-group-debt-defaults-and-state-assets-are-difficult-to-rescue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F11%2F27%2Fchinas-tewoo-group-debt-defaults-and-state-assets-are-difficult-to-rescue%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=f86ae5c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/11/27/chinas-tewoo-group-debt-defaults-and-state-assets-are-difficult-to-rescue/</a>"},{"pid":"0ff34c6ccb615dea71da40de5676c5ff4facc646","tid":1767496,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"一間爆<br />\n其他就會骨牌式跟住爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd96617b460841ee5dd8da3d0f56ba6789ed131","tid":1767496,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"講咗好多年，爆未呀"},{"pid":"7fa33769bde31f13a6aa97ae0fa596ff141b4d42","tid":1767496,"uid":28163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"國企<br />\n佢不斷開 細間國企 不停發債券<br />\n不停爆 <br />\n回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ef408043255c073d99293579ee0b64692308f5","tid":1767496,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"繼天津物產大爆炸後又第二擊"},{"pid":"6b6d8d9ba2737de8f4854aa84e81e16a381896dc","tid":1767496,"uid":291936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"方正唔係國企, 係校企"}]}